      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ACHILLES LEGEND (2) is a Colin Brennan-trained newcomer by Mobile Legend out of Rapid Reiko. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Profiles strongly for this and can make an immediate impact. HEY LACEY (5) turned in a solid run last start over 525m at The Meadows finishing 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (30.72). Yet to win here but has run some good races. Can do much better this time. THOR LEGEND (1) jumped from the middle and safely held on debut at Warrnambool over 450m (26.89). Gets the coveted rails draw for the first time. Meets a moderate line up and should do much better. ARCANE LEGEND (7) makes debut for the Colin Brennan kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
